articles.title: Dozens killed as Cyclone Freddy slams Malawi, Mozambique - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: One of the strongest cyclones ever recorded in the Southern Hemisphere hits Southern Africa for the second time.
articles.content:
Cyclone Freddy has killed more than 60 people and injured dozens in Malawi and Mozambique as it slammed into Southern Africa for the second time in a month.
